cisc275.group3.utility

Interface ConstructCrab

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSceneTests, SceneBeach, SceneBeachMini, SceneTutorial

    public interface ConstructCrab
    Interface to simplify the construction of crab objects. This code used to be within SceneBeach.java, but is transitioned into an interface to reduce code size and increase extensibility.

    ConstructCrab.java

    Author:
    Scott, Ryan, Thomas
